  "response": "Self‑interest can fuel ambition, but if it eclipses the people I care about it risks alienating patrons and tarnishing my reputation. I balance it by ensuring my work benefits those I love, keeping my brush and business grounded in community. My past misstep reminds me that unchecked self‑gain erodes trust, so I temper ambition with integrity."
